    <data key="d0">Vitesco Technologies Automated Account Vending Machine</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9-a9Y5THTYo</data>
    <data key="d2">End-to-end automated cloud landing zone using Control Tower and Step Functions to provision and configure AWS accounts across stages.</data>
